	LDAP 
	Email Extension 
	Mailer

	// Till here all Plugins Installed Successfully

	// Create First Admin User
		// Populate all the required fields like 
		// Username: devopstrainer
		// Password: ****
		// Confirm Password: ****
		// Full name: Devops
		// E-mail address: devopstrainer10@gmail.com
	
	// Click on “Save and Continue”

	// Copy the Jenkins URL: http://<PUBLIC_IP>:8080/	

	// Click on “Save and Finish”
	
	// Click on “Start using Jenkins”
	
	// HOLD FOR FEW SECONDS

	// Enter the Username and Password

	// Play with Jenkins

